---
title: Red Hot Tomato Soup with Cheesy Naan Flatbreads and Salad
description: Soup-and-salad gets a homemade upgrade with this take on the timeless combo. The centerpiece here is the tomato soup, which is as hearty and satisfying as you’d expect and then some—there’s sour cream and a pinch of chili flakes to help zhoosh it up. On the side, you’ve got a green salad with some bonus sunflower seeds (because who doesn’t love a bit of crunch). To make it complete, we’re adding cheesy flatbread toasts for your dipping and dunking pleasure.
